---
config:
  flowchart:
    htmlLabels: false
---
flowchart LR
  Update[Consent write<br>create / update / withdraw / migrate] --> API[Consent API]
  API --> Tx[(PostgreSQL transaction:<br>consent_records + consent_audit)]
  Tx --> Hot[(Hot partitions<br>monthly, 0–12 months)]
  Hot -->|nightly ETL| Warm[(S3 Standard-IA<br>12–24 months)]
  Warm -->|lifecycle policy| Cold[(S3 Glacier<br>2–5 years, jurisdiction-bound)]
  Cold -->|retention expiry| Erase[Crypto-erase or delete]
  Hot --> Query[DSAR / regulator audit<br>by consent_id, tenant, time]
  Warm --> Query
  Cold -.restore.-> Query
